General

This is the Open Source release of Lightsoft's LIDE development kit, comprising of Anvil, Fantasm and other programs. 

This source reflects a partially ported state to Mac OS X, which compiles and runs under Mac OS 8 and 9 but still has problems under Mac OS X.


